Masterchef Canada S01E12 - Line of Fire

The chefs are tasked to take over a judge's restaurant. Later, the losing team faces a pressure test making donuts.

This episode originally aired on CTV on April 7, 2014. Like all of my releases to date, the source is an analog rip, so the quality is, at best, something like A8 V8.

There are several comments online about the POKE release, saying that that file causes problems, in particular on PS3 systems. This file should work fine on any system, though as I said above, the video and audio quality isn't going to win any awards.  

To leave comments/questions for me, use kickass or thepiratebay.
